               <msContents>
                  <summary>Harp of Praise, <foreign xml:lang="gez">አርጋኖነ፡ ውዳሴ</foreign>; Two Miracles of Mary, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ተአምረ፡ ማርያም፡</foreign></summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="1r" to="146r"/>
                     <title type="complete" ref="LIT1344enzira"/>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                       በስመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ሥሉስ፡ ዘእንበበለ፡ (sic) ፍልጠት፡ ወአሐዱ፡ በጽምረት፡ ኅቡረ፡ ህላዌ፡ ዕሩየ፡ መለኮት፡...ንጽሕፍ፡ እንከ፡ ዘንተ፡ መጽሐፈ፡ ዘይሰመይ፡ አርጋኖነ፡ ውዳሴ፡ ወመሰንቆ፡ መዝሙር፡ ወእንዚራ፡ ስብሐት፡ ዘአስተብፅዖ፡ ድንግልናሃ፡...
                    </incipit>
                  </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                    <locus from="146v" to="147v"/>
                    <title ref="LIT2384Taamme"/>
                    <note>Two Miracles of Mary: <locus from="146v" to="147r"/>, How the Virgin Mary made a stream to reverse its course and water to run uphill in order to assist a poor man; <locus from="147r" to="147v"/>, How the Virgin Mary spoke from her picture to a devout worshipper and said to him, “Blessed art thou among men.”</note>
